Notes: Wes rallied from several deficits (down 32-17 in 1st half, down 65-55 in 2nd
half) to win on OT, ending MSU's 10-game win streak. Sprung tied school record
for pts in game (35) & team tied record for pts. (100). Sprung broke 86-86 tie
to give Wes lead for good at 88-86 (2:32 left) & had 3-pt. play w/1:16 left.
Game.Officials: John Antolini,  Cheryl Kraft,  Kevin Crockett
